    <h2>Meet different people that have the same passion as you</h2>
    <img src="http://speedhunters-wp-production.s3.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/01124507/paul-walker-RIP-2-1200x799.jpg" alt="Old_school_car">
